Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Palaypay Elementary School in Barangay Palaypay, in the Municipality of Anilao, Province of Iloilo, to Pascual Buyco Memorial Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 768
An Act Changing the Name of the Palaypay Elementary School in Barangay Palaypay, in the Municipality of Anilao, Province of Iloilo, to Pascual Buyco Memorial Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Palaypay Elementary School in Barangay Palaypay, in the Municipality of Anilao, Province of Iloilo, is changed to Pascual Buyco Memorial Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. The name of the Palaypay Elementary School.1awphi1
Approved: April 13, 1984
